Title: An Act Changing the Name of Jose Abad Santos Municipal High School in the Municipality of Jose Abad Santos, Province of Davao Del Sur, to Mauro Camacho Municipal High School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 747
An Act Changing the Name of Jose Abad Santos Municipal High School in the Municipality of Jose Abad Santos, Province of Davao Del Sur, to Mauro Camacho Municipal High School
Section 1. The name of Jose Abad Santos Municipal High School in the Municipality of Jose Abad Santos, Province of Davao del Sur, shall be changed to Mauro Camacho Municipal High School.1avvphi1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: April 13, 1984
